<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.3.5">
<l>paṇṭu kāma rāṉa vāṟum pāvai yarvāyamutam</l>
<l>uṇṭa vāṟum vāḻnta vāṟu mokka vuraittirumi</l>
<l>taṇṭu kālā vūṉṟi yūṉṟit taḷḷi naṭavāmuṉ</l>
<l>vaṇṭu pāṭun taṇṭu ḻāyāṉ vatari vaṇaṅkutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before I walk shuffling, poke-poking a cane as support,</l>
<l>Coughing and talking at once [about] the way I lived,</l>
<l>The way I sipped nectar from ladies’ lips, and the way I was lustful long ago,</l>
<l>We will worship at Badarī him with cool tulasī where bees hum.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
